14 0z\"></path></svg></button></div></div><div class=\"lg:hidden flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"relative\"><button class=\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white p-2 rounded-md transition-colors flex items-center justify-center\" aria-label=\"Search\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg></button></div><button>☰</button></div></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><div class=\"container-custom py-8\"><div class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">TRENDING</h2><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-medium text-sm transition-colors bg-primary text-white\">News</button><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-medium text-sm transition-colors bg-white text-neutral-700 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary\">Disease</button><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-medium text-sm transition-colors bg-white text-neutral-700 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary\">Article</button><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-medium text-sm transition-colors bg-white text-neutral-700 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary\">Lifestyle</button></div><div class=\"py-20 text-center\"><div class=\"animate-pulse\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-16 h-16 mb-4 rounded-full bg-neutral-200\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-48 h-4 mb-4 rounded bg-neutral-200\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-36 h-3 rounded bg-neutral-200\"></div></div></div></div><section class=\"mb-12\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-4\"><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1\">Health &amp; Wellness Topics</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-600\">Stay updated with wellness topics</p></div><a class=\"text-primary hover:text-primary-dark font-medium text-sm flex items-center\" href=\"/wellness\">View All<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 ml-1\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"text-center py-8\"><p class=\"text-neutral-600\">No wellness topics available at the moment.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-indigo-800 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"container-custom relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Our Medical Services</h2><p class=\"text-blue-100 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Access comprehensive healthcare services from the comfort of your home</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><a href=\"/video-consult\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group\"><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-200 transition-colors\">Video Consultation</h3><p class=\"text-blue-100 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Connect with verified doctors through secure video calls. Get instant medical advice 24/7.</p><div class=\"flex items-center text-blue-200 font-semibold group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\"><span>Book Now</span><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a href=\"/lab-tests\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group\"><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-green-200 transition-colors\">Lab Tests at Home</h3><p class=\"text-blue-100 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Book diagnostic tests with home sample collection. Get reports online within 24-48 hours.</p><div class=\"flex items-center text-green-200 font-semibold group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\"><span>Book Test</span><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a href=\"/find-doctors\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group\"><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-purple-200 transition-colors\">Find Doctors</h3><p class=\"text-blue-100 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Search and book appointments with specialist doctors near you. Read reviews and compare.</p><div class=\"flex items-center text-purple-200 font-semibold group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\"><span>Find Doctors</span><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a href=\"/find-clinics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group\"><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-200 transition-colors\">Find Clinics</h3><p class=\"text-blue-100 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Locate verified clinics and hospitals in your area. Check facilities and book appointments.</p><div class=\"flex items-center text-orange-200 font-semibold group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\"><span>Find Clinics</span><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a href=\"/surgeries\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group\"><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-400 to-red-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-red-200 transition-colors\">Medical Procedures</h3><p class=\"text-blue-100 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Expert surgeons, safe facilities, and insurance support for various medical procedures.</p><div class=\"flex items-center text-red-200 font-semibold group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\"><span>Explore Options</span><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a href=\"/medicines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group\"><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-teal-200 transition-colors\">Order Medicines</h3><p class=\"text-blue-100 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Order prescription medicines online and get them delivered to your doorstep.</p><div class=\"flex items-center text-teal-200 font-semibold group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\"><span>Order Now</span><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class=\"text-center mt-12\"><a href=\"/services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-blue-700 rounded-full font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300\"><span>View All Services</span><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 